149
00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:32,960
analyze the multiple complex

150
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,920
technical and nontechnical factors

151
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:36,980
involved in urban sanitation

152
00:07:36,980 --> 00:07:38,840
and how to prioritize them,

153
00:07:39,510 --> 00:07:42,480
and how urban sanitation
is about services

154
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:45,910
which are developed
and implemented by both public

155
